### Health Check (Root)
GET http://localhost:8000/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Health Check (Detailed)
GET http://localhost:8000/health HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### List Models
# Returns "meta-model" plus all available underlying provider models
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/models HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Get Usage Statistics
# Shows global token and request counts
GET http://localhost:8000/v1/usage HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Chat Completion (Meta-Model)
# Automatically selects the best available provider/model
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "meta-model",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "What are Medford OR known for?"}
    ],
    "temperature": 0.7
}

### Chat Completion ( Romania Inquiry )
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "meta-model",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "system", "content": "Format response in JSON."},
        {"role": "user", "content": "When was the country Romania founded?"}
    ]
}

### Specific Model Routing
# Directly target a specific provider and model
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "Mistral/mistral-large-latest",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of France?"}
    ]
}

### JSON Output Format Hint
# Injects system instructions to ensure JSON output
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "model": "meta-model",
    "messages": [
        {"role": "user", "content": "List 3 colors in a JSON array."}
    ],
    "response_format": {
        "type": "json_object"
    }
}
